title: Brazilian Jiu Jitsu Black Belt Techniques Volume 1 of 6
description:
Robson Moura shows great high level black belt Brazilian Jiu Jitsu techniques
and strategies. The great thing about these series is that Robson shows the techniques in detail so that it is impossible for the viewer to mistake himself
about a particular technique, he explains everything from the leverage to each individual grip.


In these series Robson explains all of the positions, sweeps, grips, passes
and submissions.


Volume 1: The Full GUard

Volume 2: The Robson Cross Guard

Volume 3: 100 Kilos (Side Control)

Volume 4: Attacking The Back (Turtle)

Volume 5: Butterfly Guard

Volume 6: Passing The Guard
